data.description: *GORGEOUS Mountain Views!*  Welcome to 9653 Palo Alto St. Located in a quiet neighborhood close to all amenities, schools, groceries and ranch markets! You will not want to miss out on this stunning home that offers 4 bedrooms (1 being an oversized bonus room with dual closets) 2 bathrooms, an amazing oversized kitchen and dining area that opens to a huge family room. This home has been tastefully remodeled throughout and is move-in ready. Features and upgrades include: Exterior Dunn Edwards, legendary gray, 20 year paint, updated newly painted with behr limited grey and textured feature room with added recessed led lighting, new water heater, Dual pane tinted windows, New roof, installed 6 years ago (20 year rated shingle roof), New front entry door and new front entry security gate, Custom slate porch, New back entry door leading to backyard, 220 amp upgraded power outlet in the backyard for welding or car charging. New french doors in addition room, New wood look TILE all throughout home, Guest bathroom with upgraded granite counter and natural stone shower, Master bathroom: upgraded 4 x 12 white subway tiles, new shower pan, and all new fixtures. New kitchen fully upgraded: quartz countertops, natural stone herringbone backsplash, stainless steel KitchenAid range with 5 burners, custom telescopic downdraft, stainless steel Frigidaire dishwasher, brand new stainless steel Samsung refrigerator, stainless steel farmhouse sink and a convenient spice rack cabinet by the range. Enjoy all your entertaining and hosting in this beautiful backyard with a large covered concrete patio, fresh new grass installed one year ago with raised garden beds all on automatic water systems. Fruit trees include a Pomegranate tree, tangelo tree and a large plumeria plant. A large shed in the backyard is included and make sure to bring all your toys as there is ample parking for multiple vehicles including RV's, boats and trailers!!
